solution: ```class Solution {
    public int isPrefixOfWord(String sentence, String searchWord) {
        String[] words = sentence.split(" ");
        for (int i = 0; i < words.length; i++) {
            if (words[i].startsWith(searchWord)) {
                return i + 1;
            }
        }
        return -1;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(N * M)
space complexity: O(N)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Split the sentence into words once, then scan linearly checking each word for the prefix with startsWith; return the first match index (1-based). Simple, minimal memory, and optimal for the small input constraints.

